Salinas.Alisal, Salinas, California: Alisal (also, East Salinas) (English pronunciation: /'ælˤ lɪ sælˤ/) is a neighborhood of Salinas in Monterey County, California. It is located east of downtown, at an elevation of 89 feet (27 m). The unincorporated community of Alisal was annexed to Salinas in 1963.
